Definition.WordDefinition: Unsupportable \Un`sup*port"a*ble\, a. Insupportable; unendurable. -- {Un`sup*port"a*ble*ness}, n. --Bp. Wilkins. -- {Un`sup*port"a*bly}, adv. [1913 Webster]
unsupportable adj : not able to be supported or defended
